history.created_by: /bin/sh -c set -eux; 		arch="$(apk --print-arch)"; 	case "$arch" in 		'x86_64') 			downloadUrl='https://download.java.net/java/early_access/alpine/5/binaries/openjdk-19-ea+5_linux-x64-musl_bin.tar.gz'; 			downloadSha256='0ee67a41fe97341f131bd4f065ed6092d55c15de5f00f8ba1e57d21eefb2c787'; 			;; 		*) echo >&2 "error: unsupported architecture: '$arch'"; exit 1 ;; 	esac; 		wget -O openjdk.tgz "$downloadUrl"; 	echo "$downloadSha256 *openjdk.tgz" | sha256sum -c -; 		mkdir -p "$JAVA_HOME"; 	tar --extract 		--file openjdk.tgz 		--directory "$JAVA_HOME" 		--strip-components 1 		--no-same-owner 	; 	rm openjdk.tgz*; 		rm -rf "$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts"; 	ln -sT /etc/ssl/certs/java/cacerts "$JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts"; 		java -Xshare:dump; 		fileEncoding="$(echo 'System.out.println(System.getProperty("file.encoding"))' | jshell -s -)"; [ "$fileEncoding" = 'UTF-8' ]; rm -rf ~/.java; 	javac --version; 	java --version
